reviews.text: Food is okay but too crowded and noisy during weekend. A lot of rooms to be improved for the toilets 🚾🚻and the surroundings⚕.
Good food, fair price
One of the restaurants with worst services I ever experienced

Fulum Palace is a chain restaurant, I visited one located in Hsin Kuang Sopping Centre, Wong Tai Sin yesterday.

Both the food quality and service (particularly the ratio of waiter to customer) are inferior to those of Shek Mun and Belvedere Garden of the chain for same items ordered:  dim sum and egg yoke fried rice.
A nice Cantonese restaurant.

reviews.text: 休日 朋友晚飯 沒有酒水 約$200/位。座位空間合理。
食物品質價錢合理，茶葉質素劣，早午時伙記態度差，晚飯服務態度OK
這間吾知係未就close,吾做。service n 占心狂差。吾會再幫襯。
價錢就3個人午市284,周圍都係甘就算啦，d服務呢就非常差，d服務員淨係同d熟客傾計，其他人就要叫幾次先過黎，然後有個醜樣老服務員仲要羅朱古力出黎同另外一個唔同色衫既人一起食，我地叫佢羅d野佢就哦，哦完仲要開多包黎食，睇到人火滾，然後仲要同另一個同衫既係到搭膊頭傾計，叫幾個人羅個外賣盒過黎都好似聽唔到甘，真係嫐到
